org.gvsig.fmap.dal.coverage.store.parameter

Interface RasterDataParameters

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataParameters, DataStoreParameters, DynObject, Persistent
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MultiDimensionalStoreParameters, MultiFileDataParameters, NetCDFDataParameters, RasterFileStoreParameters, TimeStoreParameters
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractNewRasterStoreParameters, AbstractRasterDataParameters, AbstractRasterFileDataParameters, BingMapsParams, ErmapperDataParameters, ErmapperNewRasterStoreParameters, GdalDataParameters, GdalNewRasterStoreParameters, GoogleMapsParams, LizardTechDataParameters, MemoryDataParameters, MultiFileDataParametersImpl, NetCDFDataParametersImpl, OSMDataParametersImpl, PostGISRasterDataParameters, TileDataParametersImpl, TileFileFormatDataParameters, TileFileFormatNewRasterStoreParameters, WCSDataParametersImpl, WMSDataParametersImpl, WMTSDataParametersImpl

    public interface RasterDataParameters
extends DataStoreParameters
    All raster parameter should inherit from this interface. It provides general methods for open a raster.
